{"tid":1791751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱黨鐵上面嗰位婆婆，我愛你","createTime":"2019-12-21T05:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T06:09:01.000Z","uid":335574,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"698512f12aad2e744603e1f807ad5e2a0c6dc79a","tid":1791751,"uid":335574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n啱啱我搭緊黨鐵<br />\n一上車就帶咗耳機<br />\n之後我就見到一位婆婆喺度用手指住部電視狂鬧<br />\n我心諗:「屌一定係啲藍絲廢老喺度鬧緊啲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n之後我就除咗耳機睇下佢講啲咩廢話<br />\n仆街點知佢喺度鬧死黑警又呃ot<br />\n喺度放催淚彈打死啲後生仔<br />\n我認真呆咗一呆<br />\n同佢對望咗一秒佢就同我講<br />\n加油呀後生仔香港冇咗你哋真係唔得<br />\n乜原來我咁似手足咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之後同佢吹咗兩句<br />\n佢講啲嘢真係好有point係典型嘅銀髮族<br />\n佢仲同我講佢去緊今日嗰個銀髮族集會<br />\n<br />\n認真聽到之後心中好激昂<br />\n婆婆你哋呢啲銀髮族都好重要㗎<br />\n我知道你有睇連登<br />\n見到嘅話喺度講聲<br />\n<br />\n不過好驚你成日咁勇喺度鬧<br />\n遲早會畀啲藍絲廢老搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91af10cf7b9863f9c63dd1f3f063bf83d7363c36","tid":1791751,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"阿婆都搞 重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dcb4e14d971a6121453f961a6ddbb74b103e66","tid":1791751,"uid":134012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"仲搭黨鐵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850bad50b35294d5bd19c7dd848237f05ea5224e","tid":1791751,"uid":71728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"搭呀 唔俾錢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b698ca12c834be580c75faf473b34f4d3c5f00eb","tid":1791751,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6dcb4e14d971a6121453f961a6ddbb74b103e66","tid":1791751,"uid":134012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"仲搭黨鐵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"免費喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1b059cff622169d58cd4f2312c2814c582b2a6","tid":1791751,"uid":256566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"睇到喊<br />\n愛妳婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a811e9b09a7c1c22647c8927b0c75c6f45cdb082","tid":1791751,"uid":89969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:07:58.000Z","msg":"多謝婆婆"},{"pid":"b4af9b8939f2f3dddfaa6f13c076b1ee7291d4cf","tid":1791751,"uid":28593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"支持銀髮"}]}